text: "One Thing Leads to Another" is a 1983 single by English new wave band the Fixx and taken from their album Reach the Beach. It is their best known song where it went to number 4 in the United States and topped the charts in Canada. ==References== Category:1983 songs Category:The Fixx songs Category:Dance-rock songs Category:Funk rock songs Category:Art rock songs
title: One Thing Leads to Another
